content_vision: Don't take me away with your love. I'm flying high single and happy here. I can't stop it, but I still want to go with you. I feel so good and soft. I'm stuck with you.
structure_suggestion_description: midtempo pop rock song with guitars and with melancholic verse and hopeful chorus
text:
Intro:
This is not a love song, it's a story of my life,
caught between chasing dreams and avoiding strife,
so take my hand and come along for the ride,
we'll hold on tight and let our hearts collide.

Chorus:
Take me away, I'll melt in your arms tonight,
just like a fever that can't be fought or denied,
I may be flying high, but I'll always come back to you,
baby, I'm stuck with you, there's nothing I can do.

Verse 1:
Always chasing thrills, never slowing down,
but when I'm with you, I wanna stay grounded.
But when I'm with you, my heart settles down,
and I realize what I truly have found,
a love that's honest, passionate and true,
baby, I'm stuck with you, and I wouldn't want it any other way.
I may be flying high, but my heart feels so light,
when I'm with you, everything just feels right.

Verse 2:
But when I'm with you, all my fears disappear,
and I know that you're the one I truly hold dear.
But with you by my side, I feel unbreakable,
like nothing can bring us down.
But when I'm stuck with you, every moment feels like a thrill,
and I never want to come down from this love high we've built.‚Äù
2. phrase:
But with you by my side, I feel unstoppable,
our love is unbreakable, it's unshakable and unstoppable.

Bridge:
And though we may face obstacles along the way,
I know our love will always lead the way,
we'll stand strong and never give in,
because my heart always knows where to begin.

'Cause being stuck with you, feels like soaring through the sky.

But now I see, I can't deny, our love was meant to be,

Verse 2:

But as the ride gets wilder, I hold on tighter,

But even when the ride gets bumpy, I wouldn't want to be anywhere else,
because your love is my safety net, my saving grace.
But as we ride this rollercoaster of love, I can't help but feel alive, with every twist and turn, it's like we're soaring to new heights. But even when the ride gets bumpy,

Bridge:

all the ups and downs were worth it for this love we have.
With you by my side, I've found my perfect ride,
every bump and turn just strengthens our love inside.

Intro:

heart racing, couldn't ignore this chemistry.

Chorus:

can't escape this hold you have on me.

Caught in the wake of your love, I surrender to your pull,
